<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='157:183'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-1a' );" name="079-1a" class="pb">[079-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='183:191'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='191:212'>　禮書綱目卷七十七　　　　　楘源江永撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='212:223'>内則　　　　曲禮二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='223:227'>　補</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='227:263'>后王命冢宰降德于衆兆民<span class='krp-note'>后君也德猶教也萬億曰/兆天子曰兆民諸侯曰萬</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='263:307'><span class='krp-note'>民周禮冢宰掌飲食司徒掌十二教今一云冢/宰記者據諸侯也諸侯并六卿為二或兼職焉</span>子事父</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='307:330'>母雞初鳴咸盥潄櫛縰笄總拂髦冠緌纓端韠紳搢笏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='330:377'><span class='krp-note'>咸皆也縰韜髪者也總束髪也垂後為飾拂髦振去塵/著之髦用髪為之象㓜時鬠其制未聞緌纓之飾也端</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='377:403'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-1b' );" name="079-1b" class="pb">[079-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='403:450'><span class='krp-note'>𤣥端士服也庶人深衣紳大帶所以自紳/約也搢猶扱也扱笏于紳笏所以記事也</span>左右佩用<span class='krp-note'>自/佩</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='450:490'><span class='krp-note'>也必佩者備/尊者使令也</span>左佩紛帨刀礪小觽金燧<span class='krp-note'>紛帨拭物之巾/也今齊人有言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='490:532'><span class='krp-note'>紛者刀礪小刀及礪礱也小觽解小結之/觽貌如錐以象骨為之金燧可取火於日</span>右佩玦捍管</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='532:573'>遰大觽木燧<span class='krp-note'>捍謂拾也言可以捍弦也管筆/彄也遰刀韠也木燧鑽火也</span>偪<span class='krp-note'>偪行/縢</span>屦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='573:601'>著綦<span class='krp-note'>綦屦/繫也</span>婦事舅姑如事父母雞初鳴咸盥潄櫛縰笄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='601:632'>總衣紳<span class='krp-note'>笄今簮也衣/紳衣而著紳</span>左佩紛帨刀礪小觽金燧右佩箴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='632:666'>管線纊施縏袠大觽木燧<span class='krp-note'>縏小嚢也縏袠言施/明為箴管線纊有之</span>衿纓綦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='666:702'>屦<span class='krp-note'>衿猶結也婦人/有纓示繫屬也</span>以適父母舅姑之所<span class='krp-note'>適/之</span>及所下氣怡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='702:728'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-2a' );" name="079-2a" class="pb">[079-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='728:759'>聲問衣燠寒疾痛疴癢而敬抑搔之<span class='krp-note'>怡悦也疴疥也/抑按瘙摩也</span>出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='759:788'>入則或先或後而敬扶持之<span class='krp-note'>先後之隨/時便也</span>進盥少者奉槃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='788:818'>長者奉水請沃盥盥卒受巾<span class='krp-note'>槃承盥水者/巾以捝手</span>問所欲而敬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='818:849'>進之柔色以温之<span class='krp-note'>温藉也承尊/者必和顔色</span>饘酏酒醴芼羮菽麥蕡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='849:880'>稲黍梁秫唯所欲<span class='krp-note'>酏粥也芼菜/也蕡熬枲實</span>棗栗飴蜜以甘之堇荁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='880:913'>枌榆免薧滫瀡以滑之脂膏以膏之<span class='krp-note'>謂用調和飲食也/荁堇類也冬用堇</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='913:951'><span class='krp-note'>夏用荁榆白曰枌免新生者薧乾/也秦人㳛曰滫齊人滑曰瀡也</span>父母舅姑必嘗之而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='951:979'>後退<span class='krp-note'>敬/也</span>　男女未冠笄者雞𥘉鳴咸盥潄櫛縰拂髦總</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='979:1005'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-2b' );" name="079-2b" class="pb">[079-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='1005:1042'>角衿纓皆佩容臭<span class='krp-note'>總角収髪結之容臭香物也以/纓佩之為廹尊者給小使也</span>昧爽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='1042:1070'>而朝<span class='krp-note'>後成/人也</span>問何食飲矣若已食則退若未食則佐長者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='1070:1098'>視具<span class='krp-note'>具饌/也</span>　凡内外雞𥘉鳴咸盥潄衣服歛枕簟灑埽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='1098:1132'>室堂及庭布席各從其事<span class='krp-note'>歛枕簟者不欲人見已/褻也簟席之親身者</span>孺子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='1132:1163'>蚤寢晏起唯所欲食無時<span class='krp-note'>孺子小子也又/後未成人者</span>　由命士以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='1163:1186'>上父子皆異宮昧爽而朝慈以㫖甘日出而退各從其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='1186:1221'>事日入而夕慈以旨甘<span class='krp-note'>異宮崇敬也慈愛敬進之日/出乃從事食禄不免農也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='1221:1244'>父母舅姑將坐奉席請何鄉將衽長者奉席請何趾少</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='1244:1270'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-3a' );" name="079-3a" class="pb">[079-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1270:1299'>者執牀與坐<span class='krp-note'>將衽謂/更卧䖏</span>御者舉几歛席與簟縣衾箧枕斂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1299:1329'>簟而襡之<span class='krp-note'>須卧乃敷之/也襡韜也</span>父母舅姑之衣衾簟席枕几不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1329:1360'>傳杖屦祗敬之勿敢近<span class='krp-note'>傳移/也</span>敦牟巵匜非餕莫敢用<span class='krp-note'>餕/乃</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1360:1399'><span class='krp-note'>用之牟讀曰堥也巵匜/酒漿器敦牟黍稷器也</span>與恒飲食非餕莫之敢飲食<span class='krp-note'>餕/乃</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1399:1436'><span class='krp-note'>食之恒常也/旦夕之常食</span>　父母在朝夕恒食子婦佐餕<span class='krp-note'>婦皆與/夫餕也</span>既</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1436:1467'>食恒餕<span class='krp-note'>每食進而盡/之未有原也</span>父没母存冡子御食羣子婦佐餕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1467:1502'>如初<span class='krp-note'>御侍也謂長子侍母食也侍/食者不餕其婦猶皆餕也</span>旨甘柔滑孺子餕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1502:1525'>父母在子雖老不坐　在父母舅姑之所有命之應唯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1525:1551'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-3b' );" name="079-3b" class="pb">[079-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1551:1578'>敬對進退周旋慎齊<span class='krp-note'>齊荘/也</span>升降出入揖遊不敢噦噫嚏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1578:1610'>咳欠伸跛倚睇視不敢唾洟<span class='krp-note'>睇傾視也易曰/明夷睇于左股</span>寒不敢襲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1610:1643'>癢不敢搔<span class='krp-note'>襲謂/重衣</span>不有敬事不敢袒裼不涉不撅<span class='krp-note'>撅揭/衣也</span>䙝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1643:1676'>衣衾不見裏<span class='krp-note'>為其/可穢</span>父母唾洟不見<span class='krp-note'>輙刷/去之</span>冠帶垢和灰請</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1676:1707'>潄衣裳垢和灰請澣<span class='krp-note'>手曰潄足曰/澣和漬也</span>衣裳綻裂紉箴請𥙷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1707:1735'>綴<span class='krp-note'>綻猶/解也</span>五日則燂湯請浴三日具沐其間面垢燂潘請</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1735:1769'>靧足垢燂湯請洗<span class='krp-note'>潘米/瀾也</span>少事長賤事貴共帥時<span class='krp-note'>共猶皆/也帥循</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1769:1799'><span class='krp-note'>也時是也禮/皆如此也</span>　子婦孝者敬者父母舅姑之命勿逆勿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1799:1825'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-4a' );" name="079-4a" class="pb">[079-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1825:1861'>怠<span class='krp-note'>朱子曰此謂不可變節以/傷尊者平日慈愛之心也</span>若飲食之雖不嗜必嘗而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1861:1896'>待<span class='krp-note'>待後命/而去也</span>加之衣服雖不欲必服而待<span class='krp-note'>待後命/釋藏也</span>加之事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1896:1925'>人代之已雖弗欲姑與之而姑使之而後復之<span class='krp-note'>朱子曰/弗欲者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1925:1960'><span class='krp-note'>慮以自逸而違命姑與姑/使者嫌於怨懟而必爭</span>子婦有勤勞之事雖甚愛之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1960:1991'>姑縱之而寧數休之<span class='krp-note'>不可愛此而/移苦於彼也</span>子婦未孝未敬勿庸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1991:2024'>疾怨<span class='krp-note'>庸之言/用也</span>姑教之若不可教而后怒之<span class='krp-note'>怒譴/責也</span>不可怒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='2024:2058'>子放婦出而不表禮焉<span class='krp-note'>表猶眀也猶為之隱/不明其犯禮之過也</span>　父母有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='2058:2081'>過下氣怡色柔聲以諌諌若不入起敬起孝説則復諌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='2081:2107'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-4b' );" name="079-4b" class="pb">[079-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='2107:2143'><span class='krp-note'>子事父母有隱/無犯起猶更也</span>不説與其得罪於鄉黨州閭寧熟諫<span class='krp-note'>子/從</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='2143:2186'><span class='krp-note'>父之令不可謂孝也周禮曰二十五家為閭/四閭為族五族為黨五黨為州五州為郷也</span>父母怒不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='2186:2213'>説而撻之流血不敢疾怨起敬起孝<span class='krp-note'>撻擊/也</span>　父母有婢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='2213:2241'>子若庶子庶孫甚愛之雖父母没没身敬之不衰<span class='krp-note'>婢子/所通</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='2241:2269'><span class='krp-note'>賤人/之子</span>子有二妾父母愛一人焉子愛一人焉由衣服飲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='2269:2296'>食由執事毋敢視父母所愛雖父母没不衰<span class='krp-note'>由自/也</span>子甚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='2296:2324'>宜其妻父母不説出<span class='krp-note'>宜猶/善也</span>子不宜其妻父母曰是善事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='2324:2347'>我子行夫婦之禮焉没身不衰　父母雖没將為善思</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='2347:2373'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-5a' );" name="079-5a" class="pb">[079-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='2373:2400'>貽父母令名必果將為不善思貽父母羞辱必不果<span class='krp-note'>貽/遺</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='2400:2435'><span class='krp-note'>也果/決也</span>　舅没則姑老<span class='krp-note'>謂傳家事/於長婦也</span>冢婦所祭祀賓客每事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='2435:2474'>必請於姑<span class='krp-note'>婦雖受傳猶/不敢專行也</span>介婦請於冢婦<span class='krp-note'>以其代姑之/事介婦衆婦</span>舅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='2474:2511'>姑使冢婦毋怠<span class='krp-note'>雖有勤勞/不敢懈倦</span>不友無禮於介婦<span class='krp-note'>衆婦無禮/冢婦不友</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='2511:2555'><span class='krp-note'>之也善兄弟為友娣姒猶兄弟也友朱子曰此/句之義未詳註説恐未然也或疑  當作敢</span>舅姑若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='2555:2585'>使介婦毋敢敵耦於冢婦<span class='krp-note'>雖有勤勞/不敢掉磬</span>不敢並行不敢並</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='2585:2619'>命不敢並坐<span class='krp-note'>下冢婦也/命為使令</span>　凡婦不命適私室不敢退<span class='krp-note'>婦/侍</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='2619:2652'><span class='krp-note'>舅姑/者也</span>婦將有事大小必請於舅姑<span class='krp-note'>不敢/專行</span>子婦無私貨無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='2652:2678'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-5b' );" name="079-5b" class="pb">[079-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='2678:2707'>私畜無私器不敢私假不敢私與<span class='krp-note'>家事統/於尊也</span>婦或賜之飲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='2707:2730'>食衣服布帛佩帨茝蘭則受而獻諸舅姑舅姑受之則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='2730:2760'>喜如新受賜<span class='krp-note'>或賜之謂/私親兄弟</span>若反賜之則辭不得命如更受</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2760:2793'>賜藏以待乏<span class='krp-note'>待舅姑之乏也不/得命者不見許也</span>婦若有私親兄弟將與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2793:2820'>之則必復請其故賜而後與之<span class='krp-note'>並内/則</span>　凡為人子之禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2820:2852'>冬温而夏凊昏定而晨省<span class='krp-note'>定安其牀衽也省/問其安否何如</span>在醜夷不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2852:2885'>爭<span class='krp-note'>醜衆也夷猶儕也四/皓曰陛下之等夷</span>　夫為人子者三賜不及車馬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2885:2932'><span class='krp-note'>三賜三命也凡仕者一命而受爵再命而受衣服三命/而受車馬車馬而身所以尊者備矣卿大夫士之子不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2932:2958'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-6a' );" name="079-6a" class="pb">[079-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2958:2995'><span class='krp-note'>受不敢以成尊比踰於父天子/諸侯之子不受自卑逺於君</span>故州閭鄉黨稱其孝也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2995:3018'>兄弟親戚稱其慈也僚友稱其弟也執友稱其仁也交</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='3018:3052'>逰稱其信也<span class='krp-note'>不敢受重賜者心也/如此而五者備有焉</span>　夫為人子者出必</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='3052:3087'>告反必面<span class='krp-note'>告面同耳反言面者從外/來宜知親之顔色安否</span>所遊必有常所習</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='3087:3120'>必有業<span class='krp-note'>縁親之意/欲知之</span>恒言不稱老<span class='krp-note'>廣/敬</span>　為人子者居不主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='3120:3154'>奥坐不中席行不中道立不中門<span class='krp-note'>謂與父同宫者也不/敢當其尊處室中西</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='3154:3199'><span class='krp-note'>南隅謂之奥道有左右中門謂棖闑之/中央内則曰由命士以上父子皆異宮</span>食饗不為概<span class='krp-note'>概/量</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='3199:3242'><span class='krp-note'>也不制待賓客/饌具之所有</span>祭祀不為尸<span class='krp-note'>尊者之處為其失子之/道然則尸卜筮無父者</span>聽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='3242:3268'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-6b' );" name="079-6b" class="pb">[079-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='3268:3298'>於無聲視於無形<span class='krp-note'>恒若親之將/有教使然</span>不登髙不臨深不苟訾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='3298:3336'>不苟笑<span class='krp-note'>為其近危辱也人之性不欲見/毁訾不欲見笑君子樂然後笑</span>孝子不服闇不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='3336:3377'>登危懼辱親也<span class='krp-note'>服事也闇㝠也不於冥闇之中從事為/卒有非常且嫌失禮也男女夜行以燭</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='3377:3410'>　父母存不許友以死<span class='krp-note'>為忘親也死/為報仇讐</span>不有私財<span class='krp-note'>並曲/禮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='3410:3441'>未仕者不敢税人如税人則以父兄之命<span class='krp-note'>不專家財也/税謂遺予人</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='3441:3471'><span class='krp-note'>弓檀/</span>　親在行禮於人稱父人或賜之則稱父拜之<span class='krp-note'>事/統</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='3471:3511'><span class='krp-note'>於尊/玉藻</span>　　父子不同席<span class='krp-note'>異尊/卑也</span>　父前子名<span class='krp-note'>對至尊無大/小皆稱名</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='3511:3540'>　子於父母則自名也<span class='krp-note'>名父母/所為也</span>　子之事親也三諫而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='3540:3566'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-7a' );" name="079-7a" class="pb">[079-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='3566:3599'>不聽則號泣而隨之<span class='krp-note'>至親無去志在感/動之  並曲禮</span>　父命呼唯而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='3599:3626'>不諾手執業則投之食在口則吐之走而不趨<span class='krp-note'>至/敬</span>親老</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='3626:3662'>出不易方復不過時<span class='krp-note'>不可以憂父母也易方為/其不信已所處也復反也</span>親癠色</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='3662:3700'>容不盛此孝子之疏節也<span class='krp-note'>言未為至孝也王季有疾文/王色憂行不能正履  玉藻</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='3700:3733'>　父母有疾冠者不櫛行不翔<span class='krp-note'>憂不為/容也</span>言不惰<span class='krp-note'>憂不在/私好</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='3733:3766'>琴瑟不御<span class='krp-note'>憂不/在樂</span>食肉不至變味飲酒不至變貌<span class='krp-note'>憂不/在味</span>笑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='3766:3803'>不至矧怒不至詈<span class='krp-note'>憂在心難變也齒/本曰矧大笑則見</span>疾止復故<span class='krp-note'>自若/常也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='3803:3835'>親有疾飲藥子先嘗之<span class='krp-note'>嘗度其/所堪</span>醫不三世不服其藥<span class='krp-note'>慎/物</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='3835:3861'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-7b' );" name="079-7b" class="pb">[079-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='3861:3902'><span class='krp-note'>齊也禮/並曲</span>　事親有隱而無犯<span class='krp-note'>隱謂不稱揚其過失也無/犯不犯顔而諫論語曰事</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='3902:3941'><span class='krp-note'>父母/幾諫</span>左右就養無方<span class='krp-note'>左右謂扶持之方猶/常也子則然無常人</span>服勤至死致</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='3941:3979'>喪三年<span class='krp-note'>勤勞辱之事也致謂戚容稱其/服也凡此以恩為制  檀弓</span>　父没而不能</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='3979:4002'>讀父之書手澤存焉耳母没而杯圈不能飲焉口澤之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='4002:4042'>氣存焉爾<span class='krp-note'>孝子見親之器物哀惻不忍用也/圈屈木所為謂巵匜之屬  玉藻</span>　為人子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='4042:4081'>者父母存冠衣不純素<span class='krp-note'>為其有喪象也純縁也玉藻曰/縞冠𤣥武子姓之冠也縞冠素</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='4081:4121'><span class='krp-note'>紕既祥之冠也深衣/曰具父母純以青</span>孤子當室冠衣不純采<span class='krp-note'>早喪親雖/除喪不心</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='4121:4165'><span class='krp-note'>哀也謂年未三十者三十壯有室有代親之端/不為孤也當室適子也深衣曰孤子衣純以素</span>　君子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='4165:4191'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-8a' );" name="079-8a" class="pb">[079-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='4191:4227'>已孤不更名<span class='krp-note'>亦重/本</span>已孤暴貴不為父作諡<span class='krp-note'>子事父無貴/賤  並曲禮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='4227:4252'>　　右事親事長<span class='krp-note'>凡聖賢論孝之言/詳見孝經篇後</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='4252:4275'>禮始於謹夫婦為宮室辨外内男子居外女子居内深</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='4275:4308'>宮固門閽寺守之男不入女不出<span class='krp-note'>閽掌中門之禁也寺/掌内人之禁令也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='4308:4341'>　男不言内女不言外<span class='krp-note'>謂事業/之次序</span>非祭非喪不相授器<span class='krp-note'>祭/嚴</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='4341:4369'><span class='krp-note'>喪遽不/嫌也</span>其相授則女受以篚其無篚則皆坐奠之而後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='4369:4397'>取之<span class='krp-note'>奠停/地也</span>外内不共井不共湢浴不通寢席不通乞假</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='4397:4425'>男女不通衣裳内言不出外言不入<span class='krp-note'>湢浴/室也</span>男子入内不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='4425:4451'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-8b' );" name="079-8b" class="pb">[079-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='4451:4482'>嘯不指夜行以燭無燭則止<span class='krp-note'>嘯讀為叱叱/嫌有隱使也</span>女子出門必</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='4482:4510'>擁蔽其面夜行以燭無燭則止<span class='krp-note'>擁猶/幛也</span>道路男子由右女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='4510:4540'>子由左<span class='krp-note'>地道尊右/  内則</span>　男女不雜坐不同椸枷不同巾櫛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='4540:4563'>不親授嫂叔不通問諸母不潄裳外言不入於梱内言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='4563:4586'>不出於梱女子許嫁纓非有大故不入其門姑姊妹女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='4586:4613'>子子已嫁而反兄弟弗與同席而坐弗與同器而食<span class='krp-note'>皆/謂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='4613:4660'><span class='krp-note'>重别防淫亂不雜坐謂男子在堂女子在房也椸可以/枷衣者通問謂相稱謝也諸母庶母也潄澣也庶母賤</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='4660:4707'><span class='krp-note'>可使潄衣不可使潄裳裳賤尊之者亦所以逺别外言/内言凡女子職也不出入者不以相問也梱門限也女</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='4707:4733'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-9a' );" name="079-9a" class="pb">[079-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='4733:4780'><span class='krp-note'>子許嫁繫纓有從人之端也大故宮中有灾變若疾病/乃後入也女子有宮者亦謂由命士以上也春秋傳曰</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='4780:4824'><span class='krp-note'>羣公子之舍則已卑矣女子十年而不出嫁乃成/人可以出矣猶不與男子共席而坐亦逺别也</span>　男</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='4824:4861'>女異長<span class='krp-note'>各自為/伯季也</span>男女非有行媒不相知名<span class='krp-note'>謂媒徃來傳/婚姻之言乃</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='4861:4896'><span class='krp-note'>相知/姓名</span>非受幣不交不親<span class='krp-note'>重别有禮/乃相纒固</span>寡婦之子非有見焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='4896:4932'>弗與為友<span class='krp-note'>辟嫌也有見謂有竒才卓/然衆人所知  並曲禮</span>　道路男子由右</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='4932:4968'>女子由左車從中央<span class='krp-note'>道中三途逺/别也  王制</span>　男女相答拜也<span class='krp-note'>嫌/逺</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='4968:4985'><span class='krp-note'>别不相答拜以/明之  曲禮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='4985:5008'>　　右男女之别　男女無媒不交無幣不相見恐男</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='5008:5034'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-9b' );" name="079-9b" class="pb">[079-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='5034:5074'>　　女之無别也<span class='krp-note'>重男女之㑹所以逺别之於禽獸也/有幣者必有媒有媒者不必有幣仲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='5074:5111'>　　<span class='krp-note'>春之月㑹男女/之時不必待幣</span>以此坊民民猶有自獻其身<span class='krp-note'>獻猶/進也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='5111:5140'>　　禮非祭男女不交爵<span class='krp-note'>交爵謂/相獻酢</span>以此坊民陽侯猶殺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='5140:5175'>　　繆侯而竊其夫人<span class='krp-note'>同姓也以貪夫人之色/至殺君而立其國未聞</span>故大饗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='5175:5209'>　　廢夫人之禮<span class='krp-note'>大饗享諸侯來朝者/也夫人之禮使人攝</span>寡婦之子不有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='5209:5241'>　　見焉則弗友也君子以辟逺也<span class='krp-note'>有見謂暏其才/藝也同志為友</span>故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='5241:5269'>　　朋友之交主人不在不有大故則不入其門<span class='krp-note'>大故/喪疾</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='5269:5296'>　　以此坊民民猶以色厚於德子云好德如好色<span class='krp-note'>此/句</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='5296:5323'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-10a' );" name="079-10a" class="pb">[079-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='5323:5362'>　　<span class='krp-note'>似不足論語曰未見好德如好色/疾時人厚於色之甚而薄於德也</span>諸侯不下漁色</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='5362:5407'>　　<span class='krp-note'>謂不内取於國中也内取國中為下漁色昏禮始/納采謂采擇其可者也國君而内取象捕魚然中</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='5407:5436'>　　<span class='krp-note'>網取之是/無所擇</span>故君子逺色以為民紀故男女授受不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='5436:5480'>　　親<span class='krp-note'>不親者不以手相與也内則曰非祭非喪不相/授器其相授則女受以篚其無篚則皆坐奠之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='5480:5517'>　　<span class='krp-note'>而後/取之</span>御婦人則進左手<span class='krp-note'>御者在右前左/手則身㣲偕之</span>姑姊妹女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='5517:5548'>　　子子已嫁而反兄弟弗與同席而坐<span class='krp-note'>女子十年而/不出也嫁及</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='5548:5587'>　　<span class='krp-note'>成人可以出矣猶不與/男子共席而坐逺别</span>寡婦不夜哭<span class='krp-note'>嫌思/人道</span>婦人疾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='5587:5618'>　　問之不以其疾<span class='krp-note'>嫌媚畧之也/問増損而已</span>以此坊民民猶淫泆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='5618:5645'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-10b' );" name="079-10b" class="pb">[079-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='5645:5677'>　　而亂於族<span class='krp-note'>亂族犯非妃/匹也  坊記</span>　淳于髠曰男女授受不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='5677:5700'>　　親禮與孟子曰禮也曰嫂溺則援之以手乎曰嫂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='5700:5723'>　　溺不援是豺狼也男女授受不親禮也嫂溺援之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='5723:5763'>　　以手者權也<span class='krp-note'>淳于姓髠名齊之辨士授與也受取/也古禮男女不親授受以逺别也援</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='5763:5805'>　　<span class='krp-note'>救之也權稱錘也稱物輕重而徃來以/取中者也權而得中是乃禮也  孟子</span>　公將有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='5805:5833'>　　行遂與姜氏如齊<span class='krp-note'>始議/行事</span>申繻曰女有家男有室無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='5833:5867'>　　相瀆也謂之有禮易此必敗<span class='krp-note'>女安夫之家夫安妻/之室違此則為瀆今</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='5867:5904'>　　<span class='krp-note'>公將姜氏如齊故知其當致/禍亂  桓十八年左氏傳</span>　鄭文夫人芊氏姜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='5904:5931'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-11a' );" name="079-11a" class="pb">[079-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='5931:5969'>　　氏勞楚子于柯澤<span class='krp-note'>楚子還過鄭鄭文公夫人芊氏/楚女姜氏齊女也柯澤鄭地名</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='5969:6002'>　　楚子使師縉示之俘馘<span class='krp-note'>師縉楚樂師也俘/所得囚馘所截耳</span>君子曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='6002:6029'>　　非禮也婦人送迎不出門見兄弟不踰閾<span class='krp-note'>閾門/限</span>戎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='6029:6068'>　　事不邇女器<span class='krp-note'>邇近也器物也言俘馘非近婦/人之物  僖二十二年左氏傳</span>　孔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='6068:6091'>　　子適季氏康子晝居内寢孔子問其所疾康子出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='6091:6114'>　　見之言終孔子退子貢問曰季孫不疾而問諸疾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='6114:6141'>　　禮與孔子曰夫禮君子不有大故則不宿於外<span class='krp-note'>大/故</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='6141:6168'>　　<span class='krp-note'>謂喪/憂</span>非致齊也非疾也則不晝夜處于内是故夜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='6168:6195'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-11b' );" name="079-11b" class="pb">[079-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='6195:6222'>　　居於外雖弔之可也晝居於内雖問其疾可也<span class='krp-note'>家/語</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='6222:6245'>　　　公父文伯之母敬姜者季康子之從祖叔母也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='6245:6278'>　　康子徃焉䦱門而與之言<span class='krp-note'>䦱闢也門/寢門也</span>皆不踰閾<span class='krp-note'>閾/門</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='6278:6322'>　　<span class='krp-note'>限也皆二人也敬姜不踰閾而出康子不踰閾而/入傳曰婦人送迎不出門見兄弟不踰閾是也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='6322:6355'>　　祭悼子康子與焉<span class='krp-note'>悼子穆伯之父敬姜/先舅也與與祭也</span>酢不受徹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='6355:6395'>　　俎不宴<span class='krp-note'>禮祭主人獻賓賓酢主人不受敬姜不/親受也祭畢徹俎又不與康子宴飲</span>宗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='6395:6436'>　　不具不繹<span class='krp-note'>繹又祭也唐尚書云祭之明日也昭謂/天子諸侯曰繹以祭之明日卿大夫曰</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='6436:6481'>　　<span class='krp-note'>賓尸與祭同日此言繹通言之也賈侍中云宗宗/臣主祭祀之禮不具謂宗臣不具在則敬姜不與</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='6481:6508'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-12a' );" name="079-12a" class="pb">[079-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='6508:6550'>　　<span class='krp-note'>繹/也</span>繹不盡飫則退<span class='krp-note'>説云飫宴安私飫也昭謂立曰/飫坐曰宴言宗具則與繹繹畢</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='6550:6586'>　　<span class='krp-note'>而飲不盡飫禮而退恐有/醉飽之失皆所以逺嫌也</span>孔子聞之曰男女之别</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='6586:6614'>　　禮之大經公父氏之婦動中禮趣度于禮矣<span class='krp-note'>國語/魯語</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='6614:6637'>男女不同椸枷不敢懸于夫之楎椸不敢藏于夫之箧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='6637:6666'>笥不敢共湢浴<span class='krp-note'>竿謂之椸/楎杙也</span>夫不在歛枕箧簟席襡器而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='6666:6696'>藏之<span class='krp-note'>不敢/䙝也</span>少事長賤事貴咸如之<span class='krp-note'>咸皆也/  内則</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='6696:6719'>　　右夫婦之别　臼季使過冀見冀缺耨其妻饁之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='6719:6752'>　　<span class='krp-note'>臼季胥臣也冀晉邑/耨鋤也野饋曰饁</span>敬相待如賓與之歸言諸文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='6752:6779'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-12b' );" name="079-12b" class="pb">[079-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='6779:6802'>　　公曰敬德之聚也能敬必有德德以治民請用之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='6802:6834'>　　臣聞之出門如賓<span class='krp-note'>如大/賓</span>承事如祭<span class='krp-note'>常謹/敬也</span>仁之則也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='6834:6849'>　　<span class='krp-note'>僖三十四/年左氏傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='6849:6879'>夫婦之禮唯及七十同藏無間<span class='krp-note'>衰老無嫌/及猶至也</span>故妾雖老年</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='6879:6916'>未滿五十必與五日之御<span class='krp-note'>五十始衰不能孕也妾閉房/不復出御矣此御謂侍夜勸</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='6916:6963'><span class='krp-note'>息也五日一御諸侯制也諸侯取九女姪娣两两而御/則三日也次两媵則四日也次夫人專夜則五日也天</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='6963:6992'><span class='krp-note'>子十五日/而一御</span>將御者齊潄澣慎衣服櫛縰笄縂角拂髦衿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='6992:7026'>纓綦屨<span class='krp-note'>其徃如朝也角衍字/也拂髦或為繆髪也</span>雖婢妾衣服飲食必後長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='7026:7053'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-13a' );" name="079-13a" class="pb">[079-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='7053:7090'>者<span class='krp-note'>人貴賤不/可以無禮</span>妻不在妾御莫敢當夕<span class='krp-note'>辟女君之御/日也  内則</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='7090:7113'>　　右御妻妾　荀子曰霜降逆女氷泮殺内十日一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='7113:7157'>　　御<span class='krp-note'>楊倞曰此盖誤耳當為氷泮逆女霜降殺内故/詩曰士如歸妻迨氷未泮殺减也内謂妾御也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='7157:7203'>　　<span class='krp-note'>十日一御即殺内之義氷泮逆女謂𤼵生之時合/男女也霜降殺内謂閉藏之時禁嗜慾也月令在</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='7203:7248'>　　<span class='krp-note'>十一月此云霜降荀卿與呂氏所聞異也鄭云歸/期謂請期也氷未泮正月中以前二月可成昏矣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='7248:7294'>　　<span class='krp-note'>故曰氷泮逆女氏朱子曰荀子本文與家語孔子/對哀公語同楊  之説恐未必然然其言霜降閉</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='7294:7327'>　　<span class='krp-note'>藏十日一御者似/亦有理故特存之</span>　晉平公有疾叔向問于子産</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='7327:7354'>　　子産曰僑聞之君子有四時朝以聽政<span class='krp-note'>聴國/政</span>晝以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='7354:7381'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-13b' );" name="079-13b" class="pb">[079-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='7381:7412'>　　訪問<span class='krp-note'>問可/否</span>夕以脩令<span class='krp-note'>念所/施</span>夜以安身于是乎節宣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='7412:7445'>　　其氣<span class='krp-note'>宣散/也</span>勿使有所壅蔽湫底以露其體<span class='krp-note'>湫集也/底滯也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='7445:7484'>　　<span class='krp-note'>露羸也壹之則血/氣集滯而體羸露</span>兹心不爽而昬亂百度<span class='krp-note'>兹此也/爽明也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='7484:7518'>　　<span class='krp-note'>百度百/事之節</span>今無乃壹之<span class='krp-note'>同四/時也</span>則生疾矣叔向曰善哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='7518:7541'>　　肸未之聞也此皆然矣晉侯求醫于秦秦伯使醫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='7541:7568'>　　和視之曰疾不可為也是謂近女室疾如蠱<span class='krp-note'>蠱惑/疾</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='7568:7597'>　　非鬼非食惑以喪志<span class='krp-note'>惑女色/而失志</span>良臣將死天命不祐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='7597:7631'>　　<span class='krp-note'>良臣不匡救君過故/將死而不為天所祜</span>公曰女不可近乎對曰節之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='7631:7658'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-14a' );" name="079-14a" class="pb">[079-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='7658:7686'>　　先王之樂所以節百事也故有五節<span class='krp-note'>五聲/之節</span>遲速本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='7686:7715'>　　末以相及中聲以降五降之後不容弹矣<span class='krp-note'>此謂先/王之樂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='7715:7747'>　　<span class='krp-note'>得中聲聲成五降/而息也降罷退</span>于是有煩手淫聲慆堙心耳乃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='7747:7781'>　　㤀平和君子弗聽也<span class='krp-note'>五降而不息則雜聲/並奏所謂鄭衛之聲</span>物亦如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='7781:7817'>　　之<span class='krp-note'>言百事皆如/樂不可失節</span>至於煩乃舍也已無以生疾<span class='krp-note'>煩不/舍則</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='7817:7850'>　　<span class='krp-note'>生/疾</span>君子之近琴瑟以儀節也非以慆心也<span class='krp-note'>為心之/節儀使</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='7850:7893'>　　<span class='krp-note'>動不/過度</span>天有六氣<span class='krp-note'>謂隂陽風/雨晦明也</span>降生五味<span class='krp-note'>謂金味辛木/味酸水味醎</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='7893:7939'>　　<span class='krp-note'>火味苦土味甘皆/由隂陽風雨而生</span>𤼵為五色<span class='krp-note'>辛色白酸色青醎色/黒苦色赤甘色黄𤼵</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='7939:7966'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-14b' );" name="079-14b" class="pb">[079-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='7966:8009'>　　<span class='krp-note'>見/也</span>徴為五聲<span class='krp-note'>白聲商青聲角黒聲羽/赤聲徴黄聲宮徴騐也</span>淫生六疾<span class='krp-note'>淫/過</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='8009:8042'>　　<span class='krp-note'>也滋味聲色所以/飬人然過則生害</span>六氣曰隂陽風雨晦明也分為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='8042:8076'>　　四時序為五節<span class='krp-note'>六氣之化分而序之則/成四時得五行之節</span>過則為菑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='8076:8113'>　　隂淫寒疾<span class='krp-note'>寒過則/為冷</span>陽淫熱疾<span class='krp-note'>熱過則/喘渴</span>風淫末疾<span class='krp-note'>末/四</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='8113:8155'>　　<span class='krp-note'>支也風/為緩急</span>雨淫腹疾<span class='krp-note'>雨濕之氣/為洩注</span>晦淫惑疾<span class='krp-note'>晦夜也為/宴寢過節</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='8155:8191'>　　<span class='krp-note'>則心/惑亂</span>明淫心疾<span class='krp-note'>明晝也思慮煩/多心勞生疾</span>女陽物而晦時淫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='8191:8225'>　　則生内熱惑蠱之疾<span class='krp-note'>女常隨男故言陽物家/道常在夜故言晦時</span>今君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='8225:8248'>　　不節不時能無及此乎出告趙孟趙孟曰誰當良</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='8248:8275'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-15a' );" name="079-15a" class="pb">[079-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='8275:8298'>　　臣對曰主是謂矣主相晉國於今八年晉國無亂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='8298:8321'>　　諸侯無闕可謂良矣和聞之國之大臣榮其寵禄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='8321:8350'>　　任其大節有菑禍興而無改焉<span class='krp-note'>改改行/以救菑</span>必受其咎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='8350:8373'>　　今君至於淫以生疾將不能圖恤社稷禍孰大焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='8373:8401'>　　主不能禦吾是以云也<span class='krp-note'>云主/將死</span>趙孟曰何謂蠱對曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='8401:8435'>　　淫溺惑亂之所生也<span class='krp-note'>溺沈没/于嗜慾</span>于文皿蟲為蠱<span class='krp-note'>文字/也皿</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='8435:8473'>　　<span class='krp-note'>器也器受蠱/害者為蠱</span>穀之飛亦為蠱<span class='krp-note'>穀乆積則變為/飛蠱名曰蠱</span>在周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='8473:8505'>　　易女惑男風落山謂之蠱䷑<span class='krp-note'>㢲下艮上蠱巽為/長女為風艮為少</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='8505:8532'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-15b' );" name="079-15b" class="pb">[079-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='8532:8572'>　　<span class='krp-note'>男為山少男而説長女非/匹故惑山木得風而落</span>皆同物也<span class='krp-note'>物謂/類也</span>趙孟曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='8572:8598'>　　良醫也厚其禮而歸之<span class='krp-note'>贈賄之禮傳昭/元年左氏</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='8598:8621'>姙子者寢不側坐不邉立不蹕不食邪味割不正不食</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='8621:8644'>席不正不坐目不視邪色耳不聽淫聲夜則令瞽誦詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='8644:8655'>道政事<span class='krp-note'>列女/傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='8655:8678'>　　右胎教　姙子之時必謹所感心感于物則其子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='8678:8701'>　　形音肖之故姙者能謹于此則生子形容端正才</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='8701:8721'>　　識必過人矣此之謂胎教<span class='krp-note'>列女/傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='8721:8748'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-16a' );" name="079-16a" class="pb">[079-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='8748:8779'>妻將生子及月辰居側室<span class='krp-note'>側室謂夾之/室次燕寢也</span>夫使人日再問</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='8779:8802'>之作而自問之妻不敢見使姆衣服而對至於子生夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='8802:8836'>復使人日再問之<span class='krp-note'>作有/感動</span>夫齊則不入側室之門<span class='krp-note'>若始時/使人問</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='8836:8867'>子生男子設弧於門左女子設帨于門右<span class='krp-note'>表男女也弧/者示有事于</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='8867:8907'><span class='krp-note'>武也帨事人/之佩巾也</span>三日始負子男射女否<span class='krp-note'>始有事也負之謂/抱之而使鄉前也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='8907:8945'>　凡接子擇日<span class='krp-note'>雖三日之内尊卑必皆選其/吉焉  接字之義見内治篇</span>冢子則大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='8945:8980'>牢<span class='krp-note'>天子世子也冢大也冢/子猶言長子通于下也</span>庶人特豚士特豕大夫少牢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='8980:9015'>國君世子大牢<span class='krp-note'>皆謂/長子</span>其非冡子則皆降一等<span class='krp-note'>謂冡子之/弟及衆妾</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='9015:9042'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-16b' );" name="079-16b" class="pb">[079-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='9042:9079'><span class='krp-note'>之子生也天子諸侯少牢大夫/特豕士特豚庶人猶特豚也</span>　異為孺子室於宫中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='9079:9108'><span class='krp-note'>特埽一處/以處之</span>擇於諸母與可者必求其寛裕慈惠温良恭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='9108:9131'>敬慎而寡言者使為子師其次為慈母其次為保母皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='9131:9175'>居子室<span class='krp-note'>此人君飬子之禮也諸母衆妾也可者傅御之/屬也子師教示以善道者慈母知其嗜慾者保</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='9175:9215'><span class='krp-note'>母安其居處者士/妻食乳之而已</span>他人無事不徃<span class='krp-note'>為兒精氣㣲/弱將驚動也</span>　大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='9215:9252'>之子有食母<span class='krp-note'>選於傅御之中喪/服所謂乳母也</span>士之喪自飬其子<span class='krp-note'>賤不/敢使</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='9252:9279'><span class='krp-note'>人/也</span>　三月之末擇日剪髪為鬌男角女羈否則男左女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='9279:9312'>右<span class='krp-note'>鬌所遺髪也夾囟/曰角午達曰覊也</span>是日也妻以子見于父貴人則為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='9312:9339'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-17a' );" name="079-17a" class="pb">[079-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='9339:9370'>衣服由命士以下皆潄澣<span class='krp-note'>貴人大夫以/上也由自也</span>男女夙興沐浴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='9370:9405'>衣服具視朔食<span class='krp-note'>朔食天子大牢諸侯少/牢大夫特豕士特豚也</span>夫入門升自阼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='9405:9435'>階立於阼西鄉妻抱子出自房當楣立東面<span class='krp-note'>入門者入/側室之門</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='9435:9471'><span class='krp-note'>也大夫以下見子就側室/見妾子于内寢辟人君也</span>姆先相曰母某敢用時日祗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='9471:9504'>見孺子<span class='krp-note'>其妻姓若言姜氏/也祗敬也或作振</span>夫對曰欽有師父執子之右</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='9504:9541'>手咳而名之<span class='krp-note'>欽敬也帥循也言教之敬使有/循也執右手明將授之事也</span>妻對曰記</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='9541:9575'>有成遂左還授師<span class='krp-note'>記猶識也識夫之言/使有成也師子師也</span>子師辯告諸婦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='9575:9610'>諸母名<span class='krp-note'>後告諸母若/名成于尊</span>妻遂適寢<span class='krp-note'>復夫之/燕寢</span>夫告宰名宰辯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='9610:9637'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-17b' );" name="079-17b" class="pb">[079-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='9637:9667'>告諸男名書曰某年某月某日某生而藏之<span class='krp-note'>宰謂屬吏/也春秋書</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='9667:9698'><span class='krp-note'>桓六年九月/丁夘子同生</span>宰告閭史閭史書為二其一藏諸閭府其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='9698:9727'>一獻諸州史州史獻諸州伯州伯命藏諸州府<span class='krp-note'>四閭為/族族百</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='9727:9770'><span class='krp-note'>家也閭胥中士一人五黨為州州二千五百家/也州長中大夫一人也皆有屬吏獻猶言也</span>夫入食</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='9770:9806'>如飬禮<span class='krp-note'>夫入已見子入室也其與妻/食如婦始饋舅姑之禮也</span>　凡名子不以國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='9806:9841'>不以日月不以隱疾不以山川<span class='krp-note'>本篇不以國在日月之/下無不以山川一句依</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='9841:9889'><span class='krp-note'>朱子取曲禮移入隱此在常語之中為後難諱也春秋/傳曰名終將諱之  疾衣中之疾也謂若黒臀黒肱矣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='9889:9928'><span class='krp-note'>疾在外者雖不得言尚可指摘此則/無時可辟俗語云隱疾為醫難也</span>大夫士之子不敢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='9928:9955'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-18a' );" name="079-18a" class="pb">[079-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='9955:9987'>與世子同名<span class='krp-note'>尊世子也其先世/子生亦勿為改</span>　妾將生子及月辰夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='9987:10010'>使人日一問之子生三月之末潄澣夙齊見於内寢禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='10010:10040'>之如始入室君已食徹焉使之特餕遂入御<span class='krp-note'>内寢適妻/寢也禮謂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='10040:10087'><span class='krp-note'>已見子夫食而使獨餕也如始入室始來嫁時妾餕夫/婦之餘亦如之既見子可以御此謂大夫士之妾也凡</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='10087:10115'><span class='krp-note'>妾稱夫/曰君</span>　庶人無側室者及月辰夫出居羣室其問之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='10115:10149'>也與子見父之禮無以異也<span class='krp-note'>夫雖辟之至問妻及見/子禮同也庶人或無妾</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='10149:10178'>凡父在孫見于祖祖亦名之禮如子見父無辭<span class='krp-note'>見子于/祖家統</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='10178:10225'><span class='krp-note'>于尊也父在則無辭有適子者無適孫與見庻子同也/父卒而有適孫則有辭與見冢子同父雖卒而庻孫猶</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='10225:10252'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-18b' );" name="079-18b" class="pb">[079-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='10252:10287'><span class='krp-note'>無辭/也</span>　由命士以上及大夫之子旬而見<span class='krp-note'>旬當為均聲/之誤也有時</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='10287:10335'><span class='krp-note'>適妾同時生子子均而見者以生先後見之既見乃食/亦辟人君也易説卦坤為均今亦或作旬也  朱子曰</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='10335:10372'><span class='krp-note'>此説疑鄭失之旬如字謂十日/也别記異聞或不待三月也</span>冢子未食而見必執其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='10372:10405'>右手適子庶子已食而見必循其首<span class='krp-note'>天子諸侯尊别世/子雖同母禮則異</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='10405:10453'><span class='krp-note'>矣未食已食急正緩庶之義也異朱子曰此承上文記/大夫禮而又别其冢適庶子之  同也冢子之禮仍與</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='10453:10474'><span class='krp-note'>前章同唯適子庶子/為異耳  並内則</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='10474:10481'>　　右生子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='10481:10519'>㓜子常視母誑<span class='krp-note'>視今之示字小未有所知常示以/正物以正教之無欺誑幼曲禮</span>　子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='10519:10546'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-19a' );" name="079-19a" class="pb">[079-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='10546:10574'>能食食教以右手能言男唯女俞男鞶革女鞶絲<span class='krp-note'>俞然/也鞶</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='10574:10621'><span class='krp-note'>小嚢盛帨巾者男用韋女用繒有飾縁之則是鞶裂/與詩云垂𢃄如厲紀子帛名裂繻字雖異意實同也</span>六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='10621:10654'>年教之数與方名<span class='krp-note'>方名東/西南北</span>七年男女不同席不共食<span class='krp-note'>蚤/其</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='10654:10685'><span class='krp-note'>别/也</span>八年出入門户及即席飲食必後長者始教之譲<span class='krp-note'>示/以</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='10685:10718'><span class='krp-note'>亷/耻</span>九年教之数日<span class='krp-note'>朔望與/六甲也</span>十年出就外傅居宿于外學</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='10718:10747'>書記衣不帛𥜗袴禮帥初朝夕學㓜儀請肄簡諒<span class='krp-note'>外傳/教學</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='10747:10795'><span class='krp-note'>師也不用帛為𥜗袴為太溫傷隂氣也禮帥初遵習先/日所為也肄習也諒信也請習簡謂所書篇數也請習</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='10795:10824'><span class='krp-note'>信謂應對/之言也</span>十有三年學樂誦詩舞勺成童舞象學射御</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='10824:10851'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-19b' );" name="079-19b" class="pb">[079-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='10851:10885'><span class='krp-note'>先學勺後學象文武之/次也成童十五以上</span>二十而冠始學禮可以衣裘帛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='10885:10917'>舞大夏惇行孝弟博學不教内而不出<span class='krp-note'>大夏樂之文武/備者也内而不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='10917:10946'><span class='krp-note'>出謂人之/謀慮也</span>三十而有室始理男事博學無方孫友視志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='10946:10991'><span class='krp-note'>室猶妻也男事授田給政役也方猶常也至此也/無常學在志所好也孫順也順于友視其所志</span>四十始</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='10991:11024'>仕方物出謀𤼵慮道合則服從不可則去<span class='krp-note'>方猶常也物/猶事也  朱</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='11024:11064'><span class='krp-note'>子曰方/猶比也</span>五十命為大夫服官政<span class='krp-note'>統一官/之政也</span>七十致事<span class='krp-note'>致其/事於</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='11064:11101'><span class='krp-note'>君而/告老</span>凡男拜尚左手<span class='krp-note'>左/陽</span>　女子十年不出<span class='krp-note'>恒居/内也</span>姆教婉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='11101:11134'>娩聴從<span class='krp-note'>婉謂言語也娩之言/媚也媚謂容貌也</span>執麻枲治絲繭織紝組紃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l349' data-llen='11134:11161'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-20a' );" name="079-20a" class="pb">[079-20a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l350' data-llen='11161:11188'>學女事以共衣服<span class='krp-note'>紃絛/也</span>觀於祭祀納酒漿籩豆菹醢禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l351' data-llen='11188:11229'>相助奠<span class='krp-note'>當及女/時而知</span>十有五年而笄<span class='krp-note'>謂應年許嫁者女子許/嫁笄而字之其未許嫁</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l352' data-llen='11229:11263'><span class='krp-note'>二十/則笄</span>二十而嫁有故二十三年而嫁<span class='krp-note'>故謂父/母之喪</span>聘則為妻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l353' data-llen='11263:11309'><span class='krp-note'>聘問也妻之言齊也以/禮聘問則得與夫敵體</span>奔則為妾<span class='krp-note'>妾之言接也聞彼有/禮走而徃焉以得接</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l354' data-llen='11309:11339'><span class='krp-note'>見于君子也/奔或為衒</span>凡女拜尚右手<span class='krp-note'>右隂也/  内則</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l355' data-llen='11339:11362'>　　右教子　孟軻之母其舍近墓孟子之少也嬉戲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l356' data-llen='11362:11385'>　　為墓間之事踊躍築埋孟母曰此非所以居子也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l357' data-llen='11385:11408'>　　乃去舍市其嬉戲為賈衒孟母曰此非所以居子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l358' data-llen='11408:11435'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0086', 'WYG', '079-20b' );" name="079-20b" class="pb">[079-20b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l359' data-llen='11435:11458'>　　也乃徙舍學宮之旁其嬉戲乃設爼豆揖讓進退</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l360' data-llen='11458:11481'>　　孟母曰此真可以居子矣遂居之孟子㓜時問東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l361' data-llen='11481:11504'>　　家殺猪何為母曰欲啖汝既而悔曰吾聞古者胎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l362' data-llen='11504:11527'>　　教今適有知而欺之是教之不信乃買猪肉以食</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l363' data-llen='11527:11546'>　　之既長就學遂成大儒<span class='krp-note'>列女/傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l364' data-llen='11546:11549'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l365' data-llen='11549:11552'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l366' data-llen='11552:11563'>　禮書綱目卷七十七</span><br/>
</p>
